# 13. Catalog QA & Drift Control\
\
At scale (100 teachers \'d7 12 books = 1,200 books), without drift control: teachers converge on same metaphors, closing lines repeat, hooks feel samey. This section prevents that.\
\
## 13.1 Metaphor Registry (Teacher Ownership)\
\
Each teacher owns 3\'965 metaphor image terms. No two teachers may share terms.\
\
```yaml\
metaphor_registry:\
  teacher_001:\
    owned_terms: [lotus, unfold, bloom, light body, golden thread]\
    forbidden_terms: [all terms owned by other teachers]\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\fs24 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 **Gate D01 (Metaphor Collision):** Teacher uses another teacher's owned term \uc0\u8594  hard fail.\
**Gate D02 (Metaphor Consistency):** Teacher uses owned terms in \uc0\u8805  6 of 12 chapters. Warn if absent.\
**Gate D03 (Metaphor Overuse):** Single term > 20 times across 12 chapters \uc0\u8594  flag.\cb1 \
\cb3 ## 13.2 Reassurance Phrase Cap\cb1 \
\cb3 No phrase may appear in > 40% of books. Monitored: "You are held," "You are not broken," "Your body knows," "Trust the process," "You are enough," "You are exactly where you need to be."\cb1 \
\cb3 **Gate D04:** Phrase in > 40% of catalog \uc0\u8594  hard fail.\
**Gate D05:** Teacher A's signature phrase in Teacher B's book \uc0\u8594  flag (contamination).\cb1 \
\cb3 ## 13.3 Hook Diversity\cb1 \
\cb3 No two books may open with the same structural pattern. Scan first 2 sentences for structure, length, opening word.\cb1 \
\cb3 **Gate D06:** Hook fingerprint similarity > 70% across catalog \uc0\u8594  hard fail.\
**Gate D07:** Teacher's 12 books all use same Opening Scene variant \uc0\u8594  flag. Require rotation.\cb1 \
\cb3 ## 13.4 Carry Line Uniqueness\cb1 \
\cb3 Final sentence of Chapter 12 = carry line. No two books may share the same carry line.\cb1 \
\cb3 **Gate D08:** Exact duplicate \uc0\u8594  hard fail.\
**Gate D09:** \uc0\u8805  50% 6-gram overlap \u8594  flag for review.\cb1 \
\cb3 ## 13.5 Emotional Waveform Entropy\cb1 \
\cb3 Each book has an intensity curve across 12 chapters. Curves should vary at catalog scale.\cb1 \
\cb3 **Gate D10:** No two books share exact same intensity sequence \uc0\u8594  flag.\
**Gate D11:** Intensity variance < 1.5 (too flat) \uc0\u8594  warn.\cb1 \
