\cb3 ## 16.8 Emotional impact patterns (misfire tax, silence beat, never-know, integration modes)\cb1 \
\cb3 These patterns are required so books have emotional voltage and visible consequence; they are enforceable via atom tags and minimum counts. Full definitions and examples: 
\f6\fs21\fsmilli10800 \cf7 \cb8 \strokec7 talp/analyze_intake/extracted_docx/EMOTIONAL_IMPACT_SPEC.md
\f0\fs24 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 .\cb1 \
\cb3 **Misfire tax:** At least one STORY atom (standard_book: \uc0\u8805 2; micro_book: \u8805 1) where the alarm or avoidance causes a visible social cost. Tag: 
\f6\fs21\fsmilli10800 \cf7 \cb8 \strokec7 misfire_tax: true
\f0\fs24 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 . QA: Something different afterward that would not have been different if the alarm had not fired.\cb1 \
\cb3 **Silence beat:** At least one moment (standard_book: \uc0\u8805 2; micro_book: \u8805 1) where a social pause is described in real time, the character experiences it somatically, resolution is ambiguous. Tag: 
\f6\fs21\fsmilli10800 \cf7 \cb8 \strokec7 silence_beat: true
\f0\fs24 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 .\cb1 \
\cb3 **Never-know:** At least one STORY atom (standard_book: \uc0\u8805 2; micro_book: \u8805 1) that ends with the character (and listener) unable to determine what the social moment meant. No resolution. Tag: 
\f6\fs21\fsmilli10800 \cf7 \cb8 \strokec7 never_know: true
\f0\fs24 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 .\cb1 \
\cb3 **Integration modes:** Five modes \'97 STILL-HERE, COST-VISIBLE, BODY-LANDED, QUESTION-OPEN, SOMEONE-ELSE. Standard_book: use \uc0\u8805 3 modes; micro_book: \u8805 2. No two consecutive chapters same mode. STILL-HERE only once per book (final chapter). Tag: 
\f6\fs21\fsmilli10800 \cf7 \cb8 \strokec7 integration_mode: still_here | cost_visible | body_landed | question_open | someone_else
\f0\fs24 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 .\cb1 \
\cb3 **Flinch audit:** Human reader reads full book at 150 WPM and marks involuntary body responses. Standard_book: \uc0\u8805 5 flinch points; micro_book: \u8805 2. Not automatable; required before approval.\cb1 \
