\f6\fs21\fsmilli10800 \cf7 \cb8 \strokec7 config/author_registry.yaml
\f0\fs24 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2  has a mandatory 
\f6\fs21\fsmilli10800 \cf7 \cb8 \strokec7 positioning_profile
\f0\fs24 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 . BookSpec carries 
