\f6\fs21\fsmilli10800 \cf7 \cb8 \strokec7 author_id
\f0\fs24 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2  is present it is resolved from the registry and must match.\cb1 \
\cb3 ## 24.1 Per-Chapter Compliance\cb1 \
\cb3 Each compiled chapter must comply with:\cb1 \
