\ls66\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 **vulnerability_band** \'97 how much first-person or confessional tone is allowed.\cb1 \
