# 14. Emotional Force Thresholds\
\
Structural validation ensures correct build. Emotional force validation ensures the book moves the listener.\
\
## 14.1 Chapter Temperature Classification\
\
| Phase | Temperature | Intensity | Requirements |\
|-------|-------------|-----------|--------------|\
| HARDSHIP | Hot | 4\'965 | Grounding verbs, body states, visible consequence |\
| HELP | Warm | 2\'963 | Teaching clarity, mechanism naming |\
| HEALING | Warm-Hot | 3\'964 | Emergence verbs, sensory present, no resolution |\
| HOPE | Cool | 1\'962 | Integration, quiet, synthesis |\
\
## 14.2 HARDSHIP Chapter Requirements (Hot)\
\
**Grounding verbs (\uc0\u8805  2):** collapse, shatter, fragment, dissolve, abandon, crumble, unravel, break, fall, lose.\
\
**Body state words (\uc0\u8805  2):** tight, numb, hollow, frozen, raw, clenched, heavy, empty, small, trapped.\
\
**Visible consequence required.** HARDSHIP chapters cannot end with "and everything was okay." Something must change, break, or stop.\
\
**Gate E01:** Grounding verbs < 2 \uc0\u8594  hard fail.\
**Gate E02:** Body state words < 2 \uc0\u8594  warn.\
**Gate E03:** Ending feels resolved \uc0\u8594  flag for rewrite.\
\
## 14.3 HEALING Chapter Requirements (Warm-Hot)\
\
**Emergence verbs (\uc0\u8805  2):** soften, open, return, notice, allow, settle, land, release, breathe, feel.\
\
**Sensory present words (\uc0\u8805  3):** breath, skin, ground, warmth, weight, texture, contact, sound, pulse, surface.\
\
**No resolution allowed.** HEALING chapters cannot end with transformation complete.\
\
**Gate E04:** Emergence verbs < 2 \uc0\u8594  warn.\
**Gate E05:** Sensory words < 3 \uc0\u8594  hard fail.\
**Gate E06:** Chapter ending implies cure \uc0\u8594  flag.\
\
## 14.4 Cognitive/Body Ratio\
\
**Formula:** cognitive_count / body_count\
\
> 5 \uc0\u8594  hard fail\
> 3 \uc0\u8594  warn\
< 2 \uc0\u8594  ideal\
## 14.5 Action \uc0\u8594  Reaction Pairing\
\
If story contains action verbs, it must contain reaction markers. Action without visible reaction feels incomplete.\
\
**Gate E08:** Action present, no reaction \uc0\u8594  hard fail.\
