\f1 \cf2 Honest view: it depends entirely on what lives in L0.\
The architecture is sound. The risk is in the execution of one layer.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\b \cf2 Where the model is safe:
\f1\b0 \
STORY atoms are fine. The "reuse" there is already happening \'97 same character cast (David, Nora, Maya), same engine logic across topics. The prose is still fully authored per atom. The modular framing just names what you're already doing.\
EXERCISE and INTEGRATION are mostly safe. Integration carry lines are short enough that L3 (micro-copy) can be genuinely authored phrase-banks, not templates. "Still here." can't be slot-filled \'97 it either lands or it doesn't, and you'll know immediately.\

\f2\b Where the model gets dangerous:
\f1\b0 \
REFLECTION. This is where the books live or die.\
The gen_z/anxiety reflections work \'97 "the Sunday feeling," "the ledger the calendar doesn't see," "the gap between what the week produced and what I was present for" \'97 because every sentence is authored at the level of the specific thing it describes. That's not L0 + L2 overlay. That's one voice going deep on one mechanism.\
If L0 becomes a skeleton \'97 "The mechanism works like this. [persona cue]. The cost looks like [cost]. You cannot see it until [insight]." \'97 and L2 swaps in "hospital shift" for "open plan office," the reader feels it immediately. The TTS flattens it. The teaching stops landing.\

\f2\b The test that tells you whether it worked:
\f1\b0 \
Read the L0 core prose out loud in a flat voice, alone \'97 without any L2 persona overlay applied. Does it still teach something specific? Does a sentence land? Or does it feel like the outline of a lesson?\
If L0 is written to the same standard as the best reflections in the current corpus \'97 specific mechanism, named cost, concrete body state \'97 then the architecture produces great books. The persona overlay adds grounding, it doesn't create the teaching.\
If L0 is a framework that L2 is supposed to make real, the books will have the shape of teaching without the substance of it.\

\f2\b Practical answer:
\f1\b0 \
The architecture buys you coverage efficiency, not prose efficiency. You still write L0 at full author quality. What you stop doing is rewriting the same mechanism insight from scratch 39 times. You write it once, deeply, then add persona specificity on top \'97 that's the real saving.\
60-70% reuse is achievable if L0 is "finished prose that works for any reader" and L2 is "the details that make it feel like it was written for this person." That's a real distinction. It won't work if L0 is a structured outline and L2 is the prose.\
Done right: same teaching quality, better coverage, faster expansion. Done wrong: faster production of books that don't land.\
