        Split at natural arc boundaries (between journey phases).\
        Each volume must stand alone as a complete therapeutic journey.\
        Volume 1 = Recognition + Mechanism Proof arcs.\
        Volume 2 = Turning Point + Embodiment arcs.\
      title_format: "\{title\} \'97 Part 1: Recognition" / "Part 2: Practice"\
